import React from 'react' import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome' import { faWind } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faMoon } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faSun } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faWater } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faEye } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faDroplet } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { faTemperatureLow } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import moment from 'moment' export default function Highlights() { const weather = useSelector(state => state.weather.weather) let timezone if(weather.length > 0){ timezone = weather[0].timezone } return (

Todays Highlights

{weather.length > 0 && !weather.loading ?

Air Quality Index

Deg

{weather[0].wind.deg}

Speed

{weather[0].wind.speed}

Sunrise & Sunset

Sunrise

{moment.utc(weather[0].sys.sunrise,'X').add(timezone,'seconds').format('HH:mm a')}

Sunset

{moment.utc(weather[0].sys.sunset,'X').add(timezone,'seconds').format('HH:mm a')}

Humidity

{weather[0].main.humidity}%

Pressure

{weather[0].main.pressure}hPa

Visibility

{weather[0].visibility / 1000}km

Feels Like

{Math.floor(weather[0].main.feels_like)}oc
:
}
) }
